    LifecycleFeature

    public final class PreDestroyLifecycleActions
extends AbstractLifecycleFeature
    Special AbstractLifecycleFeature to support @PreDestroy annotation processing. Note that this feature is implicit in LifecycleModule and therefore does not need to be added using the LifecycleFeature multibinding.
